race.description: Ladbrokes Fast Payouts Bitches Only Ht 2
race.comment: KIANDO FLORENCE (6) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 7 lengths at Muswellbrook in a handy 24.30 beating Tipsy Ethics. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can continue on her winning ways. KISS ME AUGIE (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Muswellbrook over 571m (33.15). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can measure up this time. IT'S ALL BAD (8) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (36.71) from Box 4 at Nowra over 630m. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. ZIPPING SHAYNA (4) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.
